    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>At some point in your family’s history, a dragon interbred with your bloodline. Now, the sublime monster’s ancient power fuels your bloodrage.</em><br><br><strong>Bonus Feats:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.pmAO1Sni8xx71pLF]{Blind-Fight}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.Zeq6RWYv5otvg8q7]{Cleave}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.fVRnBIHR4Jq6btvm]{Great Fortitude}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.Uuiu3p982omhMEPj]{Improved Initiative}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.FUW5mIXHNBBIQ1Sq]{Power Attack}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.7zJTztNW7hdaqjKc]{Skill Focus} (Fly),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.8snLqsJN4LLL00Nq]{Toughness}</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bonus Spells:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.sz7j540uypmqqvti]{Shield} (7th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.tkjnm3lw7ni82tag]{Resist Energy} (10th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.7d6sv5ecvi7kho3m]{Fly} (13th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.be88e90guqbi1q1z]{Fear}&nbsp;(16th)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>At 1st level, you must select one of the chromatic or metallic dragon types. Once chosen, this cannot be changed. A number of your bloodline powers deal damage and grant resistances based on your dragon type, as noted below.</p>\n<hr>\n<table class=\"inner\" style=\"border-color: white; color: #ffffff; font-family: 'Century Gothic', CenturyGothic, AppleGothic, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #0f0f0f;\">\n<tbody style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">\n<tr style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">\n<td style=\"margin: 0px; border: 1px solid white; padding: 1px 5px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">Dragon Type</strong></td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid white; padding: 1px 5px; margin: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">Energy Type</strong></td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid white; padding: 1px 5px; margin: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">Breath Shape</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: 